Filarial parasites develop faster and reproduce earlier in response to host 
immune effectors that determine filarial life expectancy.

Babayan SA(1), Read AF, Lawrence RA, Bain O, Allen JE.

Author information:
(1)Centre for Immunity, Infection and Evolution, University of Edinburgh, 
